    "spotwereld_kennisbank": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.sw-kb-wrap{padding:3.5rem 0 3rem;background:#fff}.sw-kb-inner{max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.5rem}.sw-kb-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:1rem;margin:0 0 2rem;flex-wrap:wrap}.sw-kb-head .left{max-width:680px}.sw-kb-head h2{font-size:1.85rem;font-weight:900;color:#061f40;margin:0 0 .35rem;letter-spacing:-.025em;line-height:1.15}.sw-kb-head .sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.5;margin:0}.sw-kb-cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:.4rem;color:#0F6FE3;background:#fff;border:1.5px solid #0F6FE3;padding:.7rem 1.25rem;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;text-decoration:none;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;margin-top:.4rem}.sw-kb-cta:hover{background:#0F6FE3;color:#fff;transform:translateY(-1px)}.sw-kb-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem}.sw-kb-card{position:relative;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;background:#061f40;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(6,31,64,.08);display:flex;flex-direction:column;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:all .25s ease;min-height:480px}.sw-kb-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 16px 36px rgba(6,31,64,.18)}.sw-kb-img{height:280px;background-size:cover;background-position:center;background-repeat:no-repeat;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.sw-kb-img::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent 60%,rgba(6,31,64,.15) 100%);pointer-events:none}.sw-kb-body{flex:1;padding:1.5rem 1.5rem 1.75rem;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column}.sw-kb-card .tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#bfdbfe;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.25rem .55rem;border-radius:4px;margin-bottom:.65rem;width:fit-content}.sw-kb-card h3{font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin:0 0 .65rem;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.25}.sw-kb-card p{font-size:.9rem;color:#bfdbfe;line-height:1.55;margin:0 0 1.5rem;flex:1}.sw-kb-arrow{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .2s;align-self:flex-start}.sw-kb-card:hover .sw-kb-arrow{background:#0F6FE3;border-color:#0F6FE3;transform:translateX(4px)}.sw-kb-arrow svg{color:#fff}@media(max-width:880px){.sw-kb-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:1.25rem}.sw-kb-head h2{font-size:1.5rem}.sw-kb-card{min-height:auto}.sw-kb-img{height:220px}}</style><section class=\"sw-kb-wrap\"><div class=\"sw-kb-inner\"><div class=\"sw-kb-head\"><div class=\"left\"><h2>Slim verlichten begint hier</h2><p class=\"sub\">Praktische gidsen om zelf aan de slag te gaan &mdash; van het uitzagen van een gat tot het kiezen van de juiste dimmer.</p></div><a href=\"/pages/verlichtingsgids\" class=\"sw-kb-cta\">Alle gidsen <svg width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"/></svg></a></div><div class=\"sw-kb-grid\"><a href=\"/pages/inbouwspots-plaatsen\" class=\"sw-kb-card\"><div class=\"sw-kb-img\" style=\"background-image:url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/5824517/pexels-photo-5824517.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800')\"></div><div class=\"sw-kb-body\"><span class=\"tag\">Installatie &middot; 10 min</span><h3>Inbouwspots plaatsen &mdash; stappenplan voor een strak resultaat</h3><p>Gat zagen, draadjes aansluiten en spot vastklikken. We laten zien hoe je het in &eacute;&eacute;n middag professioneel doet, zonder verrassingen achteraf.</p><div class=\"sw-kb-arrow\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"/></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/pages/led-dimmer-kiezen\" class=\"sw-kb-card\"><div class=\"sw-kb-img\" style=\"background-image:url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/3964736/pexels-photo-3964736.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800')\"></div><div class=\"sw-kb-body\"><span class=\"tag\">Tips &middot; 5 min</span><h3>De juiste LED-dimmer kiezen (en aansluiten)</h3><p>Niet elke dimmer werkt met LED. We helpen je kiezen tussen fase-aansnijding en -afsnijding, en leggen uit hoe je geflikker voorkomt.</p><div class=\"sw-kb-arrow\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"/></svg></div></div></a><a href=\"/pages/tl-naar-led\" class=\"sw-kb-card\"><div class=\"sw-kb-img\" style=\"background-image:url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/4792487/pexels-photo-4792487.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800')\"></div><div class=\"sw-kb-body\"><span class=\"tag\">Besparen &middot; 4 min</span><h3>Bespaar tot 60% door je TL te vervangen door LED-TL</h3><p>TL-buizen verbruiken veel stroom en gaan korter mee dan je denkt. Lees waarom LED-TL veel gunstiger is en hoe je de wissel in 5 minuten doet.</p><div class=\"sw-kb-arrow\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><line x1=\"5\" y1=\"12\" x2=\"19\" y2=\"12\"/><polyline points=\"12 5 19 12 12 19\"/></svg></div></div></a></div></div></section>",
